  <description type="morphology">Shrubs, spreading to erect, sparsely branched, 4–8 × 6–10 dm. Leaf blades oblanceolate to spatulate, 0.5–1.5 × 0.2–0.6 cm, mostly glabrous. Inflorescences (5–)10–20 × 5–8 cm; branches open, with numerous racemosely arranged involucres, slender and whiplike, round, smooth, glabrous, not spinose. Involucres campanulate, 1–1.5 × 1.5–3 mm. Flowers 2.5–3 mm; perianth white.</description>
